Download Etsy images and videos with one click.

# Getting Started
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension.
2. Open your target Etsy product page.
3. Click on the Etsy Image&Video Downloader icon to open it.
4. Download product images and videos.
5. Export images and video to Excel.

# Features
1.Download Images(*.jpg,*.xlsx)
2.One Click Download All Images(*.zip,*.xlsx)
3.One Click Download Videos(*.mp4,*.xlsx)

# It's free?
Yes, Etsy Image Downloader is free.
